  "section": "2.1: Quests and combat, unlock Miscellania",
  "stepText": "Continue Scorpion Catcher (catch the scorpion inside the Barbarian Outpost agility course), do a lap of the agility course for the diary. Do Horror from the Deep, kill the Dagannoth Mother w/ magic, like on the wiki. Collect a berserker ring from Dagannoth Rex (optional: stay for a dragon axe). Bring your remaining gold bars and nature runes to alch between kills (and between hits). Leave the long way to the Lighthouse for the diary, kill dagannoths on your way out for Rag and Bone Man II.\n",
